&quot;When you&rsquo;re clamping down this hard, what don&rsquo;t you like about this?&quot;

The nursery school I work for is in danger of shutting down after receiving a notice from the city hall. As a graduate of this school, I had to do something so I reached out to the person in charge, Shinomiya-san. I was supposed to get advice on how to save the school, but for some reason, I&rsquo;m in his room doing lewd things&hellip;

Even though I only wanted advice I&rsquo;m entranced by his eyelashes and enticing smell. His kiss is so erotic my brain feels like it&rsquo;s melting and his slightest touch makes me wet. Although I came for advice, I ended up getting teased until morning. Even though city officials shouldn&rsquo;t be like this, I only feel pleasure.
